{"tid":1660381,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"「納米盤業主RIP」大埔嵐山開放式獲首置客承接 165呎賣298萬","createTime":"2019-10-17T12:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T23:00:22.000Z","uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"343a5b7c962071c1e0ff5291b57f82fcbffa41c1","tid":1660381,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"美聯物業高級區域經理汪子龍表示，該行剛促成一宗大埔嵐山二手成交，一名外區上車客以298萬元，承接一個中層開放式單位，折合實用呎價約18,061元。<br />\n<br />\n剛成交單位為嵐山2座中層A室，實用面積約165平方呎，屬開放式間隔，向北望池景。汪子龍稱，買家為外區上車客，早前積極物色心儀上車單位，鍾情屋苑樓齡新，考慮不久即決定承接。原業主早年買入上址及相連B室，半年叫價約320萬元拆售上址，雙方議後價以298萬元成交。<br />\n<br />\n都係個句啦：樓市GoGoGo"},{"pid":"71f1566f14fd7cec78a26e6a33a694f9210bbca0","tid":1660381,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c2eb65db7b10984186c37a6792f17de67139f424","tid":1660381,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"終於可以入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7912cc98a52da8b005719e7e1bb5d9688e560cde","tid":1660381,"uid":183834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHHwWnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHHwWnY.jpg&h=75eefa7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f7c75d4a213838908432dd7ffe41e92fdce0802","tid":1660381,"uid":24443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"入去赤柱坐都無咁細啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772fafe37e8a5e7f161c202d90fa29e263195a44","tid":1660381,"uid":23385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"佢係連B室買<br />\n個A室買返嚟應該唔洗兩球"},{"pid":"2130dac889df00